Migration Scope

Source Environment
SQL Server 2005
Single instance architecture
Legacy OS platform
CAL-based licensing model
Physical/legacy hardware

Target Environment
SQL Server 2014
Single instance architecture
Modern OS platform
Core-based licensing model
Modern hardware or virtualized infrastructure
Centralized monitoring and governance

